<style>
body
{
background-image:url('/bgmoomin.jpg');
background-repeat:no-repeat;
background-size: cover;
}
</style>

<div style="text-align:center">
  <font color="white"><h1><br><br><br><br><br>많은 사람들이 벌써<br>그루퍼를 이용해 팀플을 시작하고 있어요</h1></font>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-4">
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-body">
          <form class="form-inline" action="/test/index" method="post">
            <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token -%>

            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputName2" placeholder="팀 이름">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">팀 만들기</button>
          </form>
          <br>
          누구나 효율적인 팀플을 원합니다. 여기 실시간 의사결정과 파일을 공유할 수 있는 서비스가 있습니다. 팀 이름을 적고 바로 이용해보세요!
          <br>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#login">로그인</button>
          <a class="btn btn-link" href="/users/sign_up" role="button">가입하기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="login" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="mySmallModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-sm">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div style="text-align:center">
        <h2>로그인</h2>
        <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="field">
            <input class="form-control" id="user_email" name="user[email]" type="email" placeholder="Email" autofocus/>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <input class="form-control" id="user_password" name="user[password]" type="password" placeholder="Password" autocomplete="off"/>
          </div>

          <% if devise_mapping.rememberable? -%>
            <div class="field">
              <%= f.check_box :remember_me %>
              <%= f.label :remember_me %>
            </div>
          <% end -%>

          <div class="fdas">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">로그인</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
